# Rendered SKILL.md files created by scripts/setup.sh and scripts/deploy.sh.
# Don't commit them — the only source of truth is templates/skill.md.template.
# The repo-local install (setup.sh option 2) renders into .claude/skills/... ;
# keeping it ignored stops it from being discovered as a duplicate skill in git.
